From: Joshua-Eisenhart <40147598+Joshua-Eisenhart@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 13:51:13 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 28/35] fix(graph): honor declared execution_profile
 frontmatter in skill source pack runner

An explicit, valid frontmatter execution_profile wins over the fuzzy
full-text heuristic; an unrecognised declaration stays undefined
instead of being silently fuzzy-matched into an undeclared family.
core/graph suite 83/83.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
